---
title: Seared Sirloin Steak & Chimichurri with Hasselback Potatoes & Argentinian Roasted Eggplant
description: A juicy tender steak is one thing, but the right condiment takes it to the next level of deliciousness. We've added a parsley and
coriander chimichurri – a bright, fresh and flavoursome sauce to give the classic steak and veg combo a flavourful upgrade.
